ProcessIndicatorPrintForm is a Form
    title is "ProcessIndicator"
    Layout
        paragraph
            last PayablesInvoiceAudit set.Status
                display as tag
                    color of blue when (AuditStatusTagBlue)
                    color of red when (AuditStatusTagRed)
                    color of green when (AuditStatusTagGreen)
            visible when (last PayablesInvoiceAudit set.ActionReason entered)
                last PayablesInvoiceAudit set.ActionReason
                    label is "Reason"
            visible when (last PayablesInvoiceAudit set.Comment entered)
                last PayablesInvoiceAudit set.Comment
                    show up to 30 characters
